cs.GT, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.SY 

This paper discusses game theory and formalism for modeling games, which falls under the category of cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory). The paper also discusses the limitations of the extensive-form game (EFG) model and proposes a solution using observations, which involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. The paper also discusses the decomposition of games, which is related to data structures (cs.DS), and the online solving of games, which is related to control systems (cs.SY).
